<p>Basically, Altcoins means "Alternate Coins" meaning other coins than more established and famous coin <a href="https://livecrypto.in/bitcoin-what-you-need-to-know-before-you-buy/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Bitcoin</a>. This term is used by Cryptizens to address the other coins which are taking up the crypto market by storm. So, the number of Altcoins in the market is more than 900 as we speak and are growing at an impressive rate.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 id="h-are-they-investable"><strong>Are they investable?</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>The answer is a simple yes. Just like Bitcoin once started these coins have a fundamentally good background and are well supported in the market. Coins like Litecoin, BTCdirect, Kraken, Bittrex have already taken the market by storm and have a good market share. So if you are late on the Bitcoin train, yes Altcoins are the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Investment" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">investment</a> you should be looking for.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 id="h-established-and-promising-altcoins"><strong>Established and Promising Altcoins</strong></h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Cardano (ADA)</strong> Cardano emerges as one of the top <a href="https://livecrypto.in/what-is-cryptocurrency-can-it-be-used-as-a-replacement-for-physical-currency/">cryptocurrencies</a> for many reasons. One is because Cardano has recorded a price momentum during the first three months of 2021. The digital coin value increased from $0.182 in early January to around $1.45 in late February and later corrected to $1.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Ethereum (ETH)</strong> Ethereum is considered fresh in the industry and has come up the list because of its advanced tech and smart contracts.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong>Dogecoin (DOGE)</strong>  Started as a meme coin and as a joke, this coin has taken the crypto world by storm and surprise. The coin has drawn international attention due to Elon Musk.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

